Okay.

269
00:18:02,357 --> 00:18:04,725
Dae Yeong just called.

270
00:18:04,725 --> 00:18:08,269
The school is going to take disciplinary action against the vice president.

271
00:18:08,269 --> 00:18:10,530
Oh, really?

272
00:18:10,530 --> 00:18:12,716
That's a relief.

273
00:18:13,952 --> 00:18:15,494
By the way, Yeon Du,

274
00:18:15,494 --> 00:18:17,304
I didn't expect that from you.

275
00:18:17,304 --> 00:18:18,531
What do you mean?

276
00:18:18,531 --> 00:18:21,551
I thought you would be dumbfounded

277
00:18:21,551 --> 00:18:24,536
and unable to speak up for yourself,

278
00:18:24,536 --> 00:18:27,239
but you stood your ground.

279
00:18:27,239 --> 00:18:31,983
I didn't expect to see your strong side.

280
00:18:31,983 --> 00:18:34,747
I'm scary when I'm angry.

281
00:18:34,747 --> 00:18:38,074
I didn't even show half of it.

282
00:18:41,086 --> 00:18:43,463
Did you just laugh at me?

283
00:18:43,463 --> 00:18:44,707
It's true.

284
00:18:44,732 --> 00:18:46,818
I'm soft on the outside but strong on the inside.

285
00:18:46,818 --> 00:18:49,902
Okay. Okay.

286
00:18:49,902 --> 00:18:52,914
Soft on the outside, strong on the inside.

287
00:18:52,914 --> 00:18:55,250
You don't believe me.

288
00:18:55,250 --> 00:18:58,270
I have to show you then.

289
00:18:58,270 --> 00:19:01,483
Senior, keep doing that a little more.

290
00:19:01,483 --> 00:19:04,185
- Doing what?
- Keep laughing at me and not believing what I say.

291
00:19:04,185 --> 00:19:06,178
Keep on doing that a little more.

292
00:19:06,178 --> 00:19:09,463
People like me are scarier when they're angry.

293
00:19:09,463 --> 00:19:13,741
You don't have to prove yourself. I believe you.

294
00:19:13,741 --> 00:19:15,737
I told you I do.

295
00:19:17,056 --> 00:19:21,692
Soft on the outside, strong on the inside.

296
00:19:21,692 --> 00:19:23,437
Why are you smiling then?

297
00:19:23,437 --> 00:19:25,896
You're laughing at me, right?

298
00:19:25,896 --> 00:19:27,666
I didn't laugh at you.

299
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:33,384
I just laughed because it's funny.

300
00:19:33,384 --> 00:19:35,991
That's the same as laughing at me.

301
00:19:35,991 --> 00:19:38,059
No.

302
00:19:38,059 --> 00:19:40,678
Admit it.

303
00:19:40,678 --> 00:19:43,420
No.

304
00:20:01,690 --> 00:20:04,950
♫ It's spreading hotter ♫

305
00:20:04,950 --> 00:20:06,970
[Next Episode]

306
00:20:06,970 --> 00:20:09,916
Can't you just take my side?

307
00:20:09,916 --> 00:20:11,027
I'm sorry.

308
00:20:11,027 --> 00:20:12,186
Seo Ju Ho.

309
00:20:12,186 --> 00:20:13,996
I'm so brazen.

310
00:20:13,996 --> 00:20:15,723
Is it really okay to just leave the rumors be?

311
00:20:15,723 --> 00:20:18,891
I thought everything would be okay, but I was wrong.

312
00:20:18,891 --> 00:20:20,344
Sorry for accusing you last time.

313
00:20:20,369 --> 00:20:22,721
You don't have to avoid me.

314
00:20:23,890 --> 00:20:26,408
You couldn't get a hold of Yeon Du?

315
00:20:26,408 --> 00:20:29,100
No way.

316
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:33,400
♫ I don't want to just hang around you, wake me up ♫

317
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:34,960
♫ Come closer to me like a fire ♫

318
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:38,571
[Best Mistake 3]
